{"tid":1653604,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阮民安多謝和勇不割席","createTime":"2019-10-14T07:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T07:09:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"22b759715b6660ff749bb6a8912438d10709abcf","tid":1653604,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191014/20786368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191014%2F20786368&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=e2631775\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191014%2F20786368&h=eb7082c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191014/20786368</a><br />\n<br />\n阮民安多謝和勇不割席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191014/large/1570972634_e31e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191014%2Flarge%2F1570972634_e31e.jpg&h=643e6f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阮民安昨日帶過百隻紙鶴參加集會，為香港人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n阮民安（Tommy）昨日到尖沙嘴出席「和理摺」摺紙鶴活動，他帶過百隻紙鶴到場，放在海濱花園草地上以紙鶴堆砌的各種口號中，他指太太要照顧兩個兒子所以不能出來。<br />\n<br />\n對於有意見認為摺紙等和理非式活動，未能支持勇武抗爭，Tommy指這是長期抗爭，不同人做不同事：「我理解手足嘅付出，多謝佢哋唔同我哋割席。不過有啲手足嘅力量溫和啲，佢哋都有佢哋嘅力量。」提到他在網上叫余文樂「躝」，Tommy指其實是想對內地人說，他表示經常收到電話騷擾被人身攻擊，但沒有甚麼大不了：「人哋一拉就拉十年，有啲冇咗性命，諗到呢度，真係唔需要為呢啲說話介懷。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：盧妹<br />\n攝影：林賓尼 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n買港鐵廣告遭網民鬧 ViuTV無阻《造星II》參賽者撐抗爭運動<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n謝安琪紅館尾場Juno做彩蛋"},{"pid":"c649669f805d037d15fbb8b3cdd5af11741334eb","tid":1653604,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:09:25.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}